[Amit Varma]: He did his schooling in Patna, went to college in Delhi, then went to the US where he joined

00:01:57.580 --> 00:02:01.400
[Amit Varma]: academia and is now a professor of English at Vassar College.

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:05.400
[Amit Varma]: He has written many books that are so varied that it is hard for me to describe them in

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:06.400
[Amit Varma]: one sentence.

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:11.600
