00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:42.480
[Amit Varma]: always lost in our smartphones, when we had the space to reflect when we had Tehraaf.

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:45.120
[Amit Varma]: The Blue Book moved me and inspired me so much.

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:46.640
[Amit Varma]: It's full of magical moments.

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:49.560
[Amit Varma]: And it's a book I will keep going back to for the rest of my life.

